OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,FScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,7,FMSPs, with almost 20% of voters still
OL,8,Fundecided ahead of the Holyrood
OL,9,Felection on Thursday, a major new poll
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FA new multilevel regression with post-
OL,13,Fstratification (MRP) poll shared
OL,14,Fexclusively with the Press Association
OL,15,Fby More in Common spoke to more than
OL,16,F4,000 Scots between March 3 and April
OL,17,F26.
