OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,FMRPs use voter intentions,
OL,7,Fdemographics, previous voting
OL,8,Fbehaviour and constituency information
OL,9,Fto project the number of seats parties
OL,10,Fcould win.
OL,12,FScottish Labour, the poll suggests,
OL,13,Fcould lose out in every local
OL,14,Fconstituency in the country, relying
OL,15,Fsolely on the regional list for the 13
OL,16,Fseats the party would win.
OL,18,FThe party has dropped four seats since
OL,19,Fa similar More in Common poll two
OL,20,Fweeks ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
