OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,FElsewhere, the SNP retains top spot,
OL,7,Fincreasing by four seats since the
OL,8,Flast poll to 60, but still five short
OL,9,Fof the majority First Minister John
OL,10,FSwinney is seeking to put more
OL,11,Fpressure on Westminster to grant
OL,12,Fanother independence referendum.
OL,14,FReform UK remains in second with a
OL,15,Fprojected 22 seats, including
OL,16,Fconstituency MSPs in Ayr and
OL,17,FBanffshire and Buchan Coast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
