OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,FThe Tories sit in joint fourth with
OL,7,Fthe Liberal Democrats on 12 seats and
OL,8,Fthe Greens would return 10 MSPs,
OL,9,Fincluding a first constituency win in
OL,10,FGlasgow Kelvin and Maryhill.
OL,12,FDespite not being projected to win a
OL,13,Fmajority, the SNP is within five
OL,14,Fpoints in five other seats, but is
OL,15,Fprojected to win 10 other local
OL,16,Fconstituencies by less than five
OL,17,Fpoints.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
