OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,FAccording to the poll, 18% of
OL,7,Frespondents said that they were
OL,8,Fundecided as the campaign enters its
OL,9,Ffinal week.
OL,11,FThe poll also suggested a widening in
OL,12,Fconstituencies, with the number of
OL,13,Fmarginal seats ` projected to be
OL,14,Fdecided by less than five points `
OL,15,Fdropping from 39 to just 15.
OL,17,FLuke Tryl, the UK director at More in
OL,18,FCommon, said the SNP looks set to win,
OL,19,Fbut the victory is "built on the
OL,20,Fcollapse of other parties rather than
OL,21,Fa surge in their own support".
OL,26,@{D@TOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
