OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"Our focus groups across Scotland find
OL,7,Fan electorate deeply uninspired by the
OL,8,Fchoices before them, and the attitude
OL,9,Fof many we have spoken to could be
OL,10,Fbest described as 'meh', which will
OL,11,Fsee the SNP limp over the finish line
OL,12,Fwith their lowest vote share in
OL,13,Fdecades," he said.
OL,15,F"Labour's position looks to be
OL,16,Fdeteriorating as the election
OL,17,Fapproaches.
OL,19,F"The party that once dominated
OL,20,FScottish politics is now projected to
OL,21,Fwin no constituency seats at all.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]wD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
