OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"This projection suggests Labour could
OL,7,Fbe facing their worst Scottish defeat
OL,8,Fsince devolution.
OL,10,F"Even where Labour is the tactical
OL,11,Fchoice to stop the SNP, unionists seem
OL,12,Funwilling to rally round Anas Sarwar's
OL,13,Fparty.
OL,15,F"One of the defining stories of this
OL,16,Felection is Reform.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
