OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"Four years ago they barely existed in
OL,7,FScottish politics ` and for a long
OL,8,Ftime it was assumed Nigel Farage's
OL,9,Fparty would not be able to break
OL,10,Fthrough north of the border.
OL,12,F"Now, they are on course to be the
OL,13,Fsecond largest party in Holyrood,
OL,14,Fovertaking Labour and the
OL,15,FConservatives, winning constituencies
OL,16,Fand picking up seats in every regional
OL,17,Flist."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
