OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,FScottish Labour deputy leader Dame
OL,7,FJackie Baillie ` who would lose the
OL,8,FDumbarton seat she has held for 27
OL,9,Fyears if the findings of the poll come
OL,10,Fto pass ` sought to brush off the poll.
OL,12,F"The only poll that matters is the
OL,13,Fvote on Thursday," she said.
OL,15,F"After nearly two decades of SNP
OL,16,Fgovernment, we have a chance to
OL,17,Fdeliver change and fix the mess they
OL,18,Fhave made of our NHS, our schools, our
OL,19,Fcommunities and our economy.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@RO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
