OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"Right across Scotland constituencies
OL,7,Fare on a knife edge and only Scottish
OL,8,FLabour can beat the SNP.
OL,10,F"The SNP's campaign has been defined
OL,11,Fby broken promises, half-baked
OL,12,Fgimmicks and desperate attempts to
OL,13,Fspread Reform lies.
OL,15,F"Reform's campaign has been a shambles
OL,16,Ffrom day one and the only thing Lord
OL,17,FOfford has a chance of winning is a
OL,18,Fyacht race with one of his six boats.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
