OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777856582
OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"A vote for either Reform or the SNP
OL,7,Fis a vote for more of the same broken
OL,8,Fstatus quo.
OL,10,F"Scottish Labour is fighting to defy
OL,11,Fthe pollsters, win this election and
OL,12,Fdeliver the change that Scotland
OL,13,Fneeds."
OL,15,FSNP campaign director Angus Robertson
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is another encouraging
OL,17,Fpoll showing a SNP majority is within
OL,18,Freach ` but there can be no room for
OL,19,Fcomplacency and we are working hard
OL,20,Ffor every vote.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@GO]xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
