OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"This poll shows growing SNP support
OL,7,Fas we are the only party focused on
OL,8,Fpeople's priorities ` taking action on
OL,9,Ffood prices, delivering a #2 bus fare
OL,10,Fcap and rolling out GP walk-in centres
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,F"Meanwhile, Labour have nothing
OL,14,Fpositive to say and are barely ahead
OL,15,Fof fifth place.
OL,17,F"They want people to vote for an
OL,18,Fopposition to stop things happening,
OL,19,Fwe are asking people to vote for an
OL,20,FSNP government to get things done.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
