OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"The best way to ensure we can deliver
OL,7,Fis by electing a majority SNP
OL,8,Fgovernment that supports people with
OL,9,Fthe cost of living, locks out Nigel
OL,10,FFarage and delivers the fresh start of
OL,11,Findependence that will bring down
OL,12,Fbills."
OL,14,FScottish Greens co-leader Gillian
OL,15,FMackay said: "If we are to build the
OL,16,Fpro-independence majority then we need
OL,17,Fto elect a record number of Scottish
OL,18,FGreen MSPs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@GO]wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
