OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777856582
OL,3,CScottish Labour could drop to just 13
OL,4,CMSPs, poll suggests
OL,6,F"Anything else risks a big backward
OL,7,Fstep and the prospect of a Labour
OL,8,FParty that will only put up more
OL,9,Fhurdles and barriers..
OL,11,F"We have shown the value of voting
OL,12,FGreen. With only seven MSPs we
OL,13,Fdelivered free bus travel for everyone
OL,14,Funder 22, an end to peak rail fares
OL,15,Fand the scrapping of school dinner
OL,16,Fdebt. With a record result we can do
OL,17,Feven more."
